35835.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
35835.description: The gang find Iroh with June's help. Iroh suggests that Zuko challenge Azula for the position of Fire Lord, with Katara to help. The others decide to intercept the airship fleet. Meanwhile, Aang comes to the conclusion that he must kill Ozai after talking to previous Avatars and finds out the island he was on was a Lion Turtle. The comet arrives at the end.

35836.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
35836.description: Sokka, Toph and Suki begin destroying the airship fleet. Aang duels Ozai, but is soon overwhelmed because of his reluctance to kill him. Zuko fights Azula in an Agni Kai, but is shot by lightning in the process of saving Katara from it.

35837.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
35837.description: SpongeBob can't drive, but you don't need a license to operate a self-driving car! // Patrick thinks he's an old man, so it's up to SpongeBob to remind him how much fun being a kid can be!

35838.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
35838.description: SpongeBob and Patrick exchange tiny living versions of themselves. It's a whole hunk of homunculus fun! // Plankton tells his Grandma that he owns the Krusty Krab, but must keep the lie going when she comes to visit.

35839.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
35839.description: The Turtles are accidentally transported to the past, and they cross paths with a familiar ninja clan.

35840.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
35840.description: Leo decides to sneak into Shredder's Lair alone only to face the biggest mutant threat yet.

35841.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
35841.description: When two Croc Bandits have a spat, it's up to Po and Mr. Ping to set things right.

35842.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
35842.description: In an attempt to get out of training, Po buys some enchanted shoes that will heighten his kung fu abilities. Unfortunately for Po, the magical shoes are evil and will soon put him and all those around him in great danger.

35843.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
35843.description: The penguins compete against the lemurs in a game of capture the flag. This should be easy for the crack penguin team, but for some mysterious reason the lemurs keep beating them to the flag. // Mort is kicked out of the lemur habitat after he touches King Julien’s feet one too many times. So, the penguins take him in and attempt to break him of his foot obsession.

35844.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
35844.description: Marlene goes over to meet the newest zoo animal, and she mysteriously disappears. The penguins and lemurs attempt to rescue her, but they are taken, too. All except for Kowalski, the last penguin standing. // When Julien is taken to the zoo infirmary for acting even weirder than usual, Maurice is left in charge. Everything goes smoothly, until suddenly Maurice is acting even crazier than Julien ever did.

35845.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
35845.description: A new secret Krabby Patty formula has disastrous results for Bikini Bottom, and only SpongeBob can save the day. // Mr. Krabs and Plankton have to take boating school classes. Thankfully, SpongeBob's there to show them the ropes!

35846.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
35846.description: When his clarinet goes missing, Squidward must become a hardboiled detective to track it down. // Squidward sends SpongeBob and Patrick on an increasingly difficult scavenger hunt to get them out of his hair.

35847.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
35847.description: SpongeBob's new friend is a giant fluffy hamster. There's one problem, though: no one else can see him! // Patrick wants to be a horse!

35848.title: Nella The Princess Knight
35848.description: When the wicked wizard steals Garrett's knightly trading cards before the big trading convention, Nella is determined to get them back. // Nella and Trinket compete to make the best ice-cream.

35849.title: Nella The Princess Knight
35849.description: Nella and the gang must avoid getting their clothes dirty before a fancy party but it proves harder than it sounds. // Nella accompanies Snowpuff the dragon on a quest to find a legendary wishing well.

35850.title: Bubble Guppies
35850.description: With an "oink, oink" here and a "moo, moo" there, the Bubble Guppies learn all about farm animals ... and discover that a lot of their favorite foods come from a farm too!

35851.title: Bubble Guppies
35851.description: The play's the thing when the Bubble Guppies go to see a production of 'The Three Little Pigs.' But when one of the actors can't perform, it's up to Deema to put on the costume and take the stage.

35852.title: Dora the Explorer
35852.description: Boots is thrilled to hear about the riddle contest today at the Tall Mountain. Who can solve the silliest riddle?

35853.title: Dora the Explorer
35853.description: Uh oh! A Big Storm Cloud is coming. Dora and Boots have to warn all their friends in the forest to get home fast so the Big Storm Cloud doesn't rain on them and get them wet.

35854.title: Rusty Rivets
35854.description: Rusty and the gang's ski trip is thwarted by a massive rockpile on the way to Pliers Peak. // Rusty and Ruby earn their camping badges by rescuing a trapped opossum.

35855.title: Rusty Rivets
35855.description: Rusty and the gang must get some penguins to the Nature Park on the hottest day of the year. // Liam enters a sand-castle building contest and loses his elaborate plans to a thieving seagull, Rusty and Ruby must get them back before the contest deadline.

35856.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
35856.description: Stripes loves his jungle horn, a special instrument that can summon all the animals in the jungle. But when a jealous Crusher steals it, Blaze and Stripes must speed after him in a wild chase to get it back.

35857.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
35857.description: Blaze discovers an exciting new sport called Truckball. But when Crusher and his team of cronies challenge him, Blaze must scour all of Axle City to put together a Truckball team before the big game.

35858.title: PAW Patrol
35858.description: An Alien Spaceship crash lands at Farmer Yumi’s! Now it’s up to the PAW Patrol to help out the stranded little extra-terrestrial by fixing his ship and getting him back to his home planet! // Marshall’s new pet frog, Smiley, is going to be in a jumping contest! The only problem is that during a practice run Smiley jumps right into Skye’s helicopter and it takes off! Now Skye and the Pups have to save Smiley!

35859.title: PAW Patrol
35859.description: Cap’n Turbot and his cousin Francois go deep sea diving to snap a picture of a rare seaslug – the only problem is their diving bell ends up stuck, and then the propeller fin breaks at the bottom of the bay! It’s PAW Patrol to the rescue, and they have just the right vehicle – Zuma’s new SUBMARINE! // A bad storm washes away Chompy the Beaver’s dam, so he starts chomping on all the wood at Farmer Yumi’s Farm! Ryder and the PAW Patrol have to fix the chomped Barn and Fence, but that’s just the beginning. Chompy has been chowing down all over town! Chase has to track the busy Beaver, while the rest of the Pups help rebuild Chompy’s home.

35860.title: PAW Patrol
35860.description: The PAW Patrol rolls out in their new PAW Patroller to save Jake when he gets stranded in the ice fields, but a new pup also pops up to lend a paw, the brave ranger, Everest!

35861.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
35861.description: Restraining SpongeBob (fka Whispering Tentacles): Annoyed by SpongeBob for the last time, Squidward issues him a restraining order. Fiasco! (fka The Priceless Patty): Plankton steals a Krabby Patty from the Krusty Krab, unaware it’s really an art piece by famous artist Fiasco.

35862.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
35862.description: Mr. Krabs manufactures Krabby Patties on an industrial scale, but it drives a wedge between SpongeBob and Patrick.

35863.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
35863.description: After Plankton drives away Mr. Krabs' customers, Mr. Krabs is forced to give out free Krabby Patties to try to win them back. // SpongeBob's pineapple is falling apart, and he needs all of his friends to help him remodel it!

35864.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
35864.description: Dr. Blowhole, uber nemesis of the Penguins, returns to New York with a plan so diabolical it plays like a symphony of evil.

35865.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
35865.description: The zoosters think King Julien has caused sweet old lady Gladys to slip and hurt herself, thus cutting off the special treats she brings for them. The rush to judgment condemns the protesting lemur to a mighty swat from the Rump Whomper. As the clock winds down to his unspeakable punishment only one abstains – Skipper’s gut inexplicably insists that King Julien is innocent. You should know better than to go against your gut. // Kowalski’s dream of attending the giant invention expo INVEXPO have to be put on hold when he’s laid up with broken legs. Skipper and the rest of the gang go in his place with the promise to bring him a full report. The injured bird goes stir crazy locked away in the hospital, however, and hallucinates that a dangerous Space Squid is invading! Could this be more than the fevered imaginings of the caged bird?

35866.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
35866.description: When Tigress discovers she's ill, Po and Monkey set out to obtain the only known cure, which is protected by the evil Scorpion.

35867.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
35867.description: After Po accidentally destroys the training hall, he seeks the help of the creator, Taotie, only to discover he's no longer a friend of kung fu... but an enemy!

35868.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
35868.description: The team discovers a Kraang ship buried under April's house where they find... April's Mom! But as April reconnects with her lost mother, is she really all that she seems?

35869.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
35869.description: An upset Mikey runs away from home and befriends a Mutant Frog in the woods. When he learns its Frog family plans to attack the human world, he has to figure out a way to stop them.

35870.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
35870.description: SpongeBob and Mr. Krabs turn an old submarine into a mobile Krusty Krab. Not to be undone by his competitor’s new gimmick, Plankton responds with his own traveling Chum Bucket. // When Patrick and SpongeBob discover they have clashing views on cleanliness, their disagreement blows up into an epic battle. Is it possible for a soap-lover like SpongeBob to ever be friends with a dirt-monger like Patrick?

35871.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
35871.description: When SpongeBob tries to spend some quality time with his friends, he just ends up being a nuisance to everyone instead. They all tell him to go away, so with a heavy heart, SpongeBob decides to do just that.

35872.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
35872.description: Squidward is rushed to the hospital when SpongeBob accidentally slams the door on Squidward’s face. He undergoes surgery to have his face fixed to look normal again – but things don’t go exactly as planned. // A very windy day in Bikini Bottom is blowing air through SpongeBob’s holes resulting in a chorus of pretty flute-like sounds. This attracts all the local Jellyfish who love the music coming out of SpongeBob.

35873.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
35873.description: Po is embarrassed when his dad takes him on a wild goose chase, but it turns out his dad is not so crazy afterall.

35874.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
35874.description: When Master Mugan from the Garnet Palace desides she needs a new Kung Fu Master, Tigress volunteers. Will the Furious Five be minus one or will Po convince Tigress to return to the Jade Palace?

35875.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
35875.description: The penguins and lemurs face off in a race. The penguins in a souped-up version of their car and the lemurs in Alice's zoo cart. Winner takes the loser's car! // Alice gives Rico a tummy-settling medicine just after he swallows a ticking time bomb.

35876.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
35876.description: As the zoo starts feeding them imitation fish cakes, the penguins take matters into their own flippers and hatch a plan to hijack a fish delivery truck. // During a particularly cold day, the rats show up and challenge the penguins to a hockey match.

35877.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
35877.description: After an accident, Donnie finds himself slowly losing his intelligence.

35878.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
35878.description: The Turtles are baited by an unknown enemy into deadly traps.

35879.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
35879.description: Plankton disguises himself as SpongeBob’s grandmother. // Mr. Krabs uses Gary to find spare change.

35880.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
35880.description: A monster terrorizes Bikini Bottom until Patrick befriends the huge creature. // SpongeBob and all the Bikini Bottom citizens disappear to an underwater resort.

35881.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
35881.description: Madame Hagfish puts a hex on the Krusty Krab. // SpongeBob and Patrick search for a legendary drain on the ocean floor.

35882.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
35882.description: When Po's friend Peng returns to the Valley of Peace, everyone is excited...except for Po. What no one else knows is that Peng is actually evil Tai Lung's nephew. Now Po has to admit to powerful Peng that he is the one who skadooshed his uncle.

35883.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
35883.description: As the annual Winter Festival approaches, Po doesn't have enough money to buy his dad the present he deserves, so he takes a job as a bounty hunter to capture a dangerous escaped convict for the reward. But Po's plan doesn't go as smooth as he hoped.

35884.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
35884.description: As the vet gathers the penguins to give them a shot, Skipper's fear of needles takes over and he goes on the run. // During a solar eclipse, Phil and Mason convince the bossy Julien that the sky spirits are angry at him. He starts acting extra-nice.

35885.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
35885.description: Mort is exposed to Kowalski's super-ray, and he grows super-big and strong. // Marlene gets a new roommate! At first, she's excited to have a new best friend. But her attitude changes when her roommate turns out to have some pretty disgusting habits.

35886.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
35886.description: Katara eventually defeats Azula by trapping her in ice, and heals Zuko. Sokka, Toph and Suki destroy the airship fleet. Aang defeats Ozai after going into the Avatar State and removes his bending abilities. Afterwards, Zuko is crowned Fire Lord. At the end, in Ba Sing Se, Aang and Katara kiss, ending the series.

35887.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
35887.description: When a young waterbender, named Katara, and her brother, Sokka, discover a giant iceberg while fishing for food around their homestead at the South Pole, they discover that there is a boy, named Aang, inside. Aang, they discover, is an airbender, (a group of people which were thought to be extinct). However, after a string of unfortunate events which puts the village in harm's way, they soon learn that there is more to him than meets the eye. Will Aang prove his hidden abilities, or will he be thought as just a child?

35888.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
35888.description: SpongeBob and Patrick fall into a cavern where frightful Trenchbillies keep them hostage. // Squidward's complaints trigger a volcanic eruption.

35889.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
35889.description: SpongeBob and Patrick dig a tunnel between their two houses and drive Squidward nuts. // Pat learns just enough karate to wreak havoc in Bikini Bottom.

35890.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
35890.description: SpongeBob, Patrick and Squidward are accidentally locked in Bikini Bottom's first time capsule. // SpongeBob and Patrick build a dream world for Squidward.

35891.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
35891.description: When Raph makes a new friend in Zog, an alien Triceraton, he may have bitten off more than he can chew.

35892.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
35892.description: When the Turtles get word of the Kraang's return, they realize there is an even bigger threat coming to Earth!

35893.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
35893.description: Po takes on the challenge of training a lovable but klutzy member of the Emperor's family. However, will Po's training be enough to protect them both from the evil designs of a traitor in their midst?

35894.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
35894.description: After dealing Taotie yet another humiliating defeat, Po is horrified to learn that the villainous warthog has had a full on nervous breakdown. Po is determined to heal his spirit and Taotie is eager to change his evil ways...or is he?

35895.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
35895.description: The rats have been terrorizing Roger the alligator. He asks the penguins for help. Their solution: swap Roger's brain with Rico's, and let the but kicking begin! // A robot is sent to the zoo to learn the habits of lemurs before it's sent into space.

35896.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
35896.description: When the penguins bring Marlene with them on a sno-cone mission in the park, she can't handle the freedom of being outside the zoo walls. // Max the cat is on the run from evil animal control Officer X, and he comes to the penguins for help.

35897.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
35897.description: When Rico gets a freaky fortune from his cookie, he initially ignores it. Julien sets out to make Rico's fortune come true. // A female chimp named Lulu arrives at the zoo for a short stay, and Phil is smitten. Unfortunately, Lulu falls for Mason.

35898.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
35898.description: SpongeBob can never say "no" to anyone, so he orders a product called the "abrasive side". // SpongeBob gets a song stuck in his head.

35899.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
35899.description: SpongeBob and Patrick play Hide N' Seek and SpongeBob searches the world for Patrick. // Plankton masquerades as Gary to steal the Krabby Patty formula.
